          <li style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Work Permits</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Bermuda Work Permits</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Every non-Bermudian who works on the island needs one.
        Here's how the system works.
      </p>
    </div>
